Jump In complete packet list

Here is the complete list of the 103 packets of the MTGA Jump In! event. Don't waste any more time and register on MTGABuddy to import your collection and check the cards you are missing!

Note that some slots in the packets are random. These slots can be occupied by 2, 3, or even 4 cards, each with its own probability of appearing.
